data.description: BEAUTIFUL! 3 Bedrooms & 3 Bathrooms Brick Front T/H with an oversized Luxury Kitchen Corian Countertop, Cherry Oak Cabinets, SS Appliances with Hardwood floors in the front foyer. This floorplan is perfect for everyday living and entertaining with a nice deck off the kitchen/dining room area. On the Lower-Level it has a Bedroom with a fireplace and bookshelves. GREAT!! location, right in the heart of Lorton Station! So many options for shopping and entertainment Amazon Fresh Grocery Store, Pohick Bay Golf Course, Lidl Grocery Store, and much more.! Coming Attractions…. Aplin X Ski Resort Within 5 min or less drive to VRE/Amtrack express, I-95, and 395 Don’t miss this opportunity!! VA Assumable loan for your new home with a 2.625% interest rate.
